---

<Layout title="Travel Grants">
	<Container>
		<Sectionhead>
			<Fragment slot="title">Travel Grants</Fragment>
			<Fragment slot="desc">Because we really want you to come!</Fragment>
		</Sectionhead>

		<div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 py-12 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
			<!-- Introduction -->
			<div class="prose prose-lg dark:prose-invert mb-12 text-justify">
				<p>
					The organizing committee is considering allocating part of the conference budget to travel grants for student presenters. 
					These grants will be assigned via an internal selection process based on qualitative and demographic criteria to ensure 
					fair and equitable distribution of available funds.
				</p>
			</div>

			<!-- Selection Criteria -->
			<div class="mb-12">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-6">Selection Criteria</h2>
				<ul class="space-y-4 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 text-justify">
					<li class="flex items-start">
						<span class="flex h-6 items-center">
							<svg class="h-5 w-5 text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
								<path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
							</svg>
						</span>
						<span class="ml-3">Peer review scores of the submitted abstract</span>
					</li>
					<li class="flex items-start">
						<span class="flex h-6 items-center">
							<svg class="h-5 w-5 text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
								<path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
							</svg>
						</span>
						<span class="ml-3">A short motivation letter or project description</span>
					</li>
					<li class="flex items-start">
						<span class="flex h-6 items-center">
							<svg class="h-5 w-5 text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
								<path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
							</svg>
						</span>
						<span class="ml-3">Academic status (e.g., pre-doctoral, with or without institutional funding)</span>
					</li>
					<li class="flex items-start">
						<span class="flex h-6 items-center">
							<svg class="h-5 w-5 text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
								<path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
							</svg>
						</span>
						<span class="ml-3">Geographic origin, prioritizing those facing high travel costs</span>
					</li>
				</ul>
			</div>

			<!-- Application Procedure -->
			<div class="mb-12">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-6">Application Procedure</h2>
				<div class="prose prose-lg dark:prose-invert text-justify">
					<p>
						There is no separate application form for travel grants. To apply, simply select the relevant option on the submission form on Oxford Abstracts. You will then be prompted to provide the following documents:
					</p>
					<ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 mt-4">
						<li>Proof of student status</li>
						<li>Proof of lack of funding (if applicable)</li>
						<li>A motivation letter (up to 500 words) explaining the relevance of participating in ConSOLE34 to your research (e.g., if the work of one of the keynote speakers particularly resonates with your own)</li>
						<li>Country of origin</li>
					</ul>
					<p class="mt-4">
						Grants will be awarded based on the above criteria.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<!-- Contact Section -->
			<div class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-6 text-justify">
				<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">Contact</h2>
				<p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
					For any questions, please contact us at{" "}
					<a href="mailto:console34@iusspavia.it" class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 hover:underline">
						console34@iusspavia.it
					</a>
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</Container>
</Layout>

<style>
  /* Add smooth scroll behavior */
  html {
    scroll-behavior: smooth;
  }
